00:20:56.710 --> 00:21:01.150
He is a good person. And why you are troubling
him? So the unconscious giving you all the

00:21:01.150 --> 00:21:04.630
time the information that you just don't do
that."

00:21:04.630 --> 00:21:11.610
And that's how he calculated what kind of
a symbol expresses what. And it was amazing,

00:21:11.610 --> 00:21:17.480
though he got his realization very late in
life, the way he discovered that there is

00:21:17.480 --> 00:21:18.920
universal unconscious.

00:21:18.920 --> 00:21:24.440
This universal unconscious is nothing but
this all-pervading power. Now it is unconscious,

00:21:24.440 --> 00:21:29.690
means it is not in our central nervous system.
We are not conscious of it. So we have to

00:21:29.690 --> 00:21:35.140
be conscious of it. How do we get conscious
of it is that, first we have to get connected

00:21:35.140 --> 00:21:41.170
to our Spirit because spirit is the expression
of that universal unconscious within us or

00:21:41.170 --> 00:21:46.640
you can say the link. Unless and until you
get your Self-Realization you cannot be linked,

00:21:46.640 --> 00:21:53.580
you cannot be linked with this universal power
which is within us as Kundalini and which

00:21:53.580 --> 00:21:55.960
is without all over.

00:21:55.960 --> 00:22:02.960
It is most surprising to understand that God
who has created us with such care with such

00:22:03.510 --> 00:22:10.070
love, especially as a human being which is
the most beautiful thing God has created.

00:22:10.070 --> 00:22:15.250
We may or may not think so. We may not. We
may have self-pity; we may have guilt, all

00:22:15.250 --> 00:22:19.770
these nonsensical ideas. But you don't know.
You're special thing that God has created.

00:22:19.770 --> 00:22:26.220
And on top of that the highest human being
are not these politicians, or these great

00:22:26.220 --> 00:22:33.010
successes, and geniuses, and all that but
who? These are the seekers because they have

00:22:33.010 --> 00:22:37.940
to enter into the kingdom of God. It is their
right first to enter into the kingdom of God.

00:22:37.940 --> 00:22:44.940
They are a very, very special category. And
this is very well described by a great poet

00:22:45.670 --> 00:22:52.670
William Blake, who says that these are men
of God. And he described the modern times

00:22:53.760 --> 00:22:55.310
and Sahaja Yoga very well.

00:22:55.310 --> 00:23:01.320
He says, "These men of God will be born in
those days, and they will become prophets,

00:23:01.320 --> 00:23:07.060
and they will have powers to make others prophets."
And that's the thing he said.

00:23:07.060 --> 00:23:13.860
Then when you go to any seeking or any one
you must know, "Have you become your own master?"

00:23:13.860 --> 00:23:20.130
You must have the mastery. Supposing you want
to learn a car driving, a simple thing like

00:23:20.130 --> 00:23:25.360
that, you should know how to drive the car.
Supposing you go to somebody for any seeking,

00:23:25.360 --> 00:23:31.160
you must know, "Have you been able to drive
yourself all right towards seeking?" For example,

00:23:31.160 --> 00:23:36.750
I've seen people who just start jumping. When
I went to India, there was gentleman who was

00:23:36.750 --> 00:23:39.450
sitting, and he put his feet forward like
that.

00:23:39.450 --> 00:23:43.090
So people said, "You can't put your feet towards
Mother. That's not proper."

00:23:43.090 --> 00:23:46.870
He said, "Oh, God. If I put my feet backwards,
I will start jumping like a frog."

00:23:46.870 --> 00:23:49.980
I said, "How? Why? What has happened to you?"

00:23:49.980 --> 00:23:56.100
He said, "My Kundalini is awakened by my guru,
and he says after Kundalini is awakened you

00:23:56.100 --> 00:23:57.080
start jumping like a frog."

00:23:57.080 --> 00:24:02.890
And he showed Me in the book this fellow had
written that you start jumping like a frog.

00:24:02.890 --> 00:24:06.600
Can you imagine? It was written in the book.

00:24:06.600 --> 00:24:11.860
I said, "Are you going become now frogs or
earthworms? Are you going to jump like that,

00:24:11.860 --> 00:24:17.270
like a monkey or a frog? Are you going to
bark like a dog?" You are going to become

00:24:17.270 --> 00:24:23.810
a super human being. You are not going to
be driven by these forces, these are all negative

00:24:23.810 --> 00:24:28.480
forces, which control you and make you mad
like this.

00:24:28.480 --> 00:24:33.540
You have to understand everything when you
get your realization, every word of it. It's

00:24:33.540 --> 00:24:39.450
so logical; it's so practical as he says.
It is so practical, and it is so wonderful.

00:24:39.450 --> 00:24:45.890
Gavin Brown who came here first, was one of
the first Sahaja Yogis I had in London. And

00:24:45.890 --> 00:24:51.350
you know English people are rather difficult
to crack, I mean, rather difficult people.

00:24:51.350 --> 00:24:56.410
But they are first class. I mean that's the
good thing because they do not get exposed

00:24:56.410 --> 00:25:02.880
to so many nonsenses that some people who
are open can get you. And once they get realization

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:05.580
they're really top class people.

00:25:05.580 --> 00:25:11.000
Now this gentleman when he got realization,
he said, "Mother, you said we can be collectively

00:25:11.000 --> 00:25:13.340
conscious. I can't believe it. How can I become?"

00:25:13.340 --> 00:25:17.600
I said, "If I tell you about the television,
you won't believe Me till I put it to the

00:25:17.600 --> 00:25:21.870
mains. You see anybody will think it's just
a box. But you are a great instrument, and

00:25:21.870 --> 00:25:23.770
you have started working."

00:25:23.770 --> 00:25:27.670
He said, "All right! I am rather worried about
my father. He didn't telephone to me all these

00:25:27.670 --> 00:25:27.920
days."

00:25:27.910 --> 00:25:31.870
I said, "All right. You just telephone to
him and find out." I said, "First of all see

00:25:31.870 --> 00:25:34.450
your vibrations."
He said, "Mother, I'm getting a burning here,

00:25:34.450 --> 00:25:35.010
a terrible burning."

00:25:35.010 --> 00:25:38.640
Now these are the centers for your father,
right hand side, these are the centers.

00:25:38.640 --> 00:25:44.220
So, I said "All right. That means, this center
that means he must be down with a very bad

00:25:44.220 --> 00:25:45.520
bronchitis."

00:25:45.520 --> 00:25:49.280
He telephoned, and the mother came in, and
she said, "I am sorry your father is down

00:25:49.280 --> 00:25:50.150
with very bad bronchitis."

00:25:50.150 --> 00:25:57.150
This telecommunication, this divine power
knows everything. It understands everything.

00:25:58.180 --> 00:26:05.180
It knows you very well because it has created
you. It organizes everything, it cooperates

00:26:05.900 --> 00:26:12.900
everything, it puts everything into integration,
it works out everything. It works out so many

00:26:14.060 --> 00:26:19.490
things, even material things it works out;
even getting a ticket, it will work out. It's

00:26:19.490 --> 00:26:24.520
so helpful; all the angels are there. Just
to see all that, to witness it itself is so

00:26:24.520 --> 00:26:30.750
great. From lowest to the highest, it works
out everything for you. And the whole, the

00:26:30.750 --> 00:26:37.750
sum total, the unity of it is that it is love.
So it is so kind, it is so compassionate,

00:26:39.480 --> 00:26:44.840
it looks after you. It, you see, hobnobs with
you little bit, you see, gives you little

00:26:44.840 --> 00:26:48.650
lesson here and there, but it never allows
you to be ruined. It gives you little lessons

00:26:48.650 --> 00:26:54.110
if you do wrong; it teaches you little bit
then again it brings you back. It is so loving,

00:26:54.110 --> 00:26:59.010
so kind. Specially for people who are just
realized, are like small little children like

00:26:59.010 --> 00:27:05.340
seedlings. It looks after. It guides you very
much, it helps you so much. It's such a wonderful

00:27:05.340 --> 00:27:09.510
thing to be with it, and the whole thing looks
like a fun, like a drama.

00:27:09.510 --> 00:27:16.510
I went to see a gentleman called Harban in
New York, and he had three children born realized.

00:27:19.500 --> 00:27:24.610
One was about seven, another was about five,
and the little one was about three years.

00:27:24.610 --> 00:27:28.530
And all one better than the other with sparkling
eyes just waiting for Me.

00:27:28.530 --> 00:27:33.170
And when I reached there they said, "Mother,
aren't there three eyes we have got?"

00:27:33.170 --> 00:27:34.970
I said, "Yes, where?"

00:27:34.970 --> 00:27:39.520
"One here, one here, and one there. And daddy
doesn't believe me."

00:27:39.520 --> 00:27:44.060
And this one of these gurus has told him wrong
that there is only one eye. No there are three,

00:27:44.060 --> 00:27:48.210
three are centers here actually. And they
argue with their father.

00:27:48.210 --> 00:27:50.460
And they said, "Mother, aren't you tired?"

00:27:50.460 --> 00:27:51.760
I said, "Why?"

00:27:51.760 --> 00:27:57.320
"We are tired now because we are watching
the story bit too much. We should finish now."

00:27:57.320 --> 00:28:04.160
Just imagine. Small children of seven years
and five years are talking like this. My own

00:28:04.160 --> 00:28:09.700
grandchildren are realized souls, and they
are so wonderful that the one who was three

00:28:09.700 --> 00:28:14.040
years of age went to school, and everywhere
these days they are selling God. So in the

00:28:14.040 --> 00:28:19.700
school they gave some papers they are saying
that, in the paper was saying so, that if

00:28:19.700 --> 00:28:24.510
you come to a particular hotel and pay about
