00:28:24.510 --> 00:28:29.940
So she looked at Me, she said, "Transformation
is not possible till you get your Kundalini

00:28:29.940 --> 00:28:31.280
up there, up here."

00:28:31.280 --> 00:28:36.390
I said, "It's true. It has to happen but they
are saying like this."

00:28:36.390 --> 00:28:41.310
But the elder one says, "It is not possible.
They are saying, 'You can give a course.'

00:28:41.310 --> 00:28:45.110
How can you give you course? My father has
done fourteen courses. His Kundalini has not

00:28:45.110 --> 00:28:49.670
risen as yet. If by courses if you can raise
the Kundalini then my father's Kundalini should

00:28:49.670 --> 00:28:49.920
