00:29:40.300 --> 00:29:43.740
She said, "You get down from there, you are
not a realized soul, you should not allow

00:29:43.740 --> 00:29:45.090
anybody to touch your feet."

00:29:45.090 --> 00:29:51.230
Can you imagine a five-year-old child saying
that? It happens. These children are coming

00:29:51.230 --> 00:29:56.390
up within ten years you'll see. They are the
edifice, they are the complete structure,

00:29:56.390 --> 00:30:00.690
but you are the foundations of these great
work, you are the foundations.

00:30:00.690 --> 00:30:05.370
So you must get your realization, that's the
main thing. You must get your realization.

