will work out. So first of all you must get

00:30:21.750 --> 00:30:27.340
your realization. And as you get realized
all these problems get mostly solved by themselves

00:30:27.340 --> 00:30:34.340
because, why do we take to alcoholism or to
drugs? Either for seeking or for escaping.

00:30:34.560 --> 00:30:38.600
Because you are so bored with yourself and
with others that you take to these things,

00:30:38.600 --> 00:30:42.910
absolutely it is the expression of boredom.
